    public static enum VeluxKLFAPI.Command
extends java.lang.Enum<VeluxKLFAPI.Command>
    Enumeration of complete API as definition of a List of Gateway commands.

    See Appendix 3: List of Gateway commands

    Methods available:

    • Constructor VeluxKLFAPI.Command by String.
    • Method getCommand to return a VeluxKLFAPI.CommandNumber.
    • Method getDescription to return a description as String.
    • Method get to return a VeluxKLFAPI.Command based on the given int.
